title: #607: The Lost Tribes of Israel with El DeRado
description:
Welcome to a special preview of killer content you get on the Tin Foil Hat's Secret Society of The Mad Hatters. This episode Sam discusses the history of the Lost Tribes of Israel with High School friend Tony DeRado. Plus we feature Kyle James's song "IIluminati" at the end. If you enjoy Kyle's song please click on the Soundcloud link to check out some more of his work. Thank you all of your support. Happy Memorial Day weekend everyone.
Thank you so much for your support and enjoy your Memorial Day weekend.
